data.description: Your dream of coastal living begins here! Nestled just minutes from the pristine beaches of Gulf Shores, this property offers the perfect blend of coastal living and modern comfort. Whether you're a first-time homebuyer, seeking a second home, or looking for a lucrative investment opportunity, this recently updated gem is sure to captivate your heart. Embrace the coastal lifestyle to the fullest with grocery stores, restaurants, and shopping hubs within easy reach. Your everyday necessities and indulgences are moments away. Recent renovations have graced this residence with fresh paint, new flooring, and elegant cabinetry in both the kitchen and bathrooms. The granite countertops and brand-new appliances.  Don't miss your chance to experience the Gulf Shores lifestyle at its finest. Schedule a viewing today and let this newly renovated, prime location property become the backdrop for your coastal dreams.
